                    <dd class="- topic/dd " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/add_ons_for_technical_documentation.dita" xtrc="dd:3;41:25">Convert various formats like Word, HTML, Markdown, DocBook, Open API, or
                        Confluence into other formats like DITA XML.</dd>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry class="- topic/dlentry " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/add_ons_for_technical_documentation.dita" xtrc="dlentry:4;44:26">
                    <dt class="- topic/dt " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/add_ons_for_technical_documentation.dita" xtrc="dt:4;45:25"><xref href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-addons/topics/git-addon.html" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/add_ons_for_technical_documentation.dita" xtrc="xref:5;46:60"><?ditaot usertext?>Git Client add-on</xref></dt>
                    <dd class="- topic/dd " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/add_ons_for_technical_documentation.dita" xtrc="dd:4;47:25">Collaborate with your colleagues on a Git project. Comes with support for: <ul class="- topic/ul " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/add_ons_for_technical_documentation.dita" xtrc="ul:2;47:104">
                            <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/add_ons_for_technical_documentation.dita" xtrc="li:4;48:33">Git Staging<ul class="- topic/ul " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/add_ons_for_technical_documentation.dita" xtrc="ul:3;48:48">
                                    <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/add_ons_for_technical_documentation.dita" xtrc="li:5;49:41">Settings to validate before commit or before push.</li>
                                </ul></li>
                            <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/add_ons_for_technical_documentation.dita" xtrc="li:6;51:33">Git History</li>
                            <li class="- topic/li " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/add_ons_for_technical_documentation.dita" xtrc="li:7;52:33">Git Branch Manager</li>
                        </ul></dd>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry class="- topic/dlentry " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/add_ons_for_technical_documentation.dita" xtrc="dlentry:5;55:26">
                    <dt class="- topic/dt " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/add_ons_for_technical_documentation.dita" xtrc="dt:5;56:25"><xref href="https://www.oxygenxml.com/doc/ug-addons/topics/content-fusion-addon.html" format="html" scope="external" class="- topic/xref " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/add_ons_for_technical_documentation.dita" xtrc="xref:6;58:60"><?ditaot usertext?>Content Fusion Connector
                        Add-on</xref></dt>
                    <dd class="- topic/dd " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/add_ons_for_technical_documentation.dita" xtrc="dd:5;60:25">Create review tasks for collaborators and subject matter experts who can
                        later review the tasks in a web browser.</dd>
                </dlentry>
                <dlentry class="- topic/dlentry " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/add_ons_for_technical_documentation.dita" xtrc="dlentry:6;63:26">
