                        Add-on</xref></dt>
                    <dd class="- topic/dd " xtrf="file:/D:/syncprojects/blog/topics/add_ons_for_technical_documentation.dita" xtrc="dd:6;68:25">View and manage comments made in the Oxygen WebHelp Feedback forms directly
                        in the Oxygen application.</dd>
                </dlentry>
